review_body: Brought it on vacation for a week and one of the straps is already tearing.

review_headline: Great bag for the boat and/or beach
review_body: This is a great bag for a day on the beach. It is not waterproof, but it is not supposed to be. I use it every weekend and like the size and simple style.
The material is a little cheaply made, however for the price, that is expected.
Gave as a gift! Loved it!
